      Pinjarra Hills is the quiet end of Brisbane's prestige acreage corridor. The suburb is dominated by large landholdings, frequently between 2 and 10 hectares, with established residences, equestrian facilities and significant landscape investment. Buyers here are not in a hurry. They are looking for the right property, and they have specific lifestyle and infrastructure requirements that need to be matched precisely.
    </p>
