    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Pinjarra Hills.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Pinjarra Hills?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Pinjarra Hills property values are driven by acreage size, the quality of the residence, equestrian or rural infrastructure, and proximity to the Brisbane River. Larger holdings on usable cleared land, properties with dressage facilities, stables or arenas, and prestige homes with elevated outlooks command the strongest premiums in this market.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Pinjarra Hills?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Pinjarra Hills properties typically sell within 45 to 75 days. This is a considered prestige acreage market where the right buyer often comes from interstate, an interstate executive relocation or a strategic upgrade decision, so campaigns benefit from longer exposure to a national audience.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Pinjarra Hills?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Pinjarra Hills offers one of Brisbane's most exclusive acreage lifestyles, with most holdings between 2 and 10 hectares. Equestrian facilities are common, the suburb is bordered by the Brisbane River and Moggill Conservation Park, and residents enjoy genuine rural seclusion within 25 minutes of the Western Freeway and the inner-city corridor.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Pinjarra Hills a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Pinjarra Hills remains one of the most tightly held acreage suburbs in Brisbane. Limited supply, the rarity of usable acreage at this proximity to the CBD, and consistent demand from prestige and equestrian buyers have produced steady long-term capital growth. It is a market that rewards quality holdings and considered selling strategy.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

